Detailed Description

cvmx_sso_rwq_head_ptr#

CSR reserved addresses: (24): 0xb040..0xb0f8 CSR align addresses: =========================================================================================================== SSO_RWQ_HEAD_PTRX = SSO Remote Queue Head Register (one per QOS level) Contains the ptr to the first entry of the remote linked list(s) for a particular QoS level. SW should initialize the remote linked list(s) by programming SSO_RWQ_HEAD_PTRX and SSO_RWQ_TAIL_PTRX to identical values.
